{"tid":1640320,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黎依間日式餐廳好想俾香港人瘋狂懲罰!","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:09:38.000Z","uid":1806,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9677f6ca579a50ae77e39bb40a6d093c8166f7","tid":1640320,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3piOAmM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3piOAmM.jpg&h=a67acfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以支持下依一間日本餐廳叫「大丼家」。<br />\nFacebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TsuenWan.KOLOUR.2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTsuenWan.KOLOUR.2%2F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=e2291cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TsuenWan.KOLOUR.2/</a><br />\n<br />\n食完之後發現張單上面都會印有「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油，萬事小心!</span></strong>」和「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></strong>」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然咁支持香港人，黎緊依幾日都瘋狂去幫襯，懲罰到佢地生意做唔停手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>地址：荃灣眾安街68號荃灣千色匯II期地下G1-2號舖</strong><br />\n<br />\nShare Facebook Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/photos/a.113270736678204/136602847678326/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2Fphotos%2Fa.113270736678204%2F136602847678326%2F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=a52d48e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/photos/a.113270736678204/136602847678326/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">支持教育電視好簡單，希望你地繼續關注運動發展，大家齊上齊落，支持我地既前線<br />\n同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">Telegram Channel 現已啟用</span>，用你十秒時間入黎Like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />晒我地開左既社交媒體AC就得, 多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/fa